The '''Cartann Ground Champion''' was the officially recognized top [[blastsword]] duelist in the [[Adumar/Legends|Adumari]] nation of [[Cartann]]. The title was earned by winning the annual [[Cartann Ground Championship]] or by defeating the current champion in a duel. Becoming Ground Champion was the only way for a non-[[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] to attain wealth and status in Cartann. In [[13 ABY/Legends|13 ABY]], the Cartann Ground Champion was [[Cheriss ke Hanadi]]. She was succeeded by [[Thanaer ke Sekae]], who defeated her in a title match.

